branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The CXS-R Series is a dual piston actuator with non-rotating accuracy &#xb1; 0.1&#xb0; enhanced with a retract end lock feature for added machine safety. The end lock will engage when air pressure is lost and can be released by reintroducing air pressure or via a manual release bolt. The CXSL-R high precision ball bushing bearing type allows for smooth operation that ensures stable travel resistance.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bore sizes: 6, 10, 15, 20, 25, 32mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-rotating accuracy: &amp;plusmn; 0.1&amp;deg;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stroke lengths up to 100mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

